                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Longinius <lb n="2"/>Vale<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ar</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apo</abbr><ex>llinaris</ex></expan> ve<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>teran</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXXX <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nach dem Fund 1830 &amp;quot;&amp;quot;sofort zertrümmert und als Baustein in das Marchfeld gebracht&amp;quot;&amp;quot; (CIL 03, 04475). Lesung nach CIL 03, 04475. Zeile 1: NI-Ligatur; Zeile 2: VA-Ligatur; Zeile 3: MIL-, AP-, VE-Ligatur; Zeile 4: AN-Ligatur. Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Rosette und stehende Ganzfigur (CIL). (B): Z. 4: Vorbeck: ter[a]n(us).</p>
            </div>
